snippet.title: Why Amber Feels so Bad to Play (Gameplay Design Analysis)
snippet.description:
I explain why I think Amber's kit feels bad to play with, not why she is "bad." I discuss why the problem goes beyond just her numbers, and has more to with how her gameplay is designed.
